source.name: 2009 Freedom of Information Act (FOIA) Annual Report
source.description: This file contains the Social Security Administration's 2009 FOIA Annual Report.  The report provides detailed information regarding the number and type of FOIA cases we processed in FY 2009.  It also includes data regarding time and costs associated with processing these cases.
